---
import photoPlaceholder from '../assets/pipe-lights/placeholder.svg';
import pipeRender from '../assets/pipe-lights/pipe_render.png';
import pipeLights from '../assets/pipe-lights/pipe_lights.jpg';

const shell =
	"min-h-dvh bg-white dark:bg-zinc-950 font-[system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe_UI','Helvetica_Neue',Arial,sans-serif] text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-50 **:box-border";
const eyebrow = 'text-[0.6875rem] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-500';
---

<div class={shell}>
	<header class="border-b border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 bg-white/90 dark:bg-zinc-950/90 backdrop-blur-sm">
		<div
			class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4 px-6 py-4"
		>
			<a
				href="/product-design"
				class="text-sm text-zinc-500 transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400 dark:hover:text-zinc-50"
			>
				← Product design
			</a>
			<p class={`m-0 ${eyebrow}`}>1.2 Pipe lights</p>
		</div>
	</header>

	<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pt-12 pb-10 sm:pt-16 sm:pb-14">
		<p class={`m-0 ${eyebrow}`}>1.2 Pipe lights</p>
		<h1 class="m-0 mt-2 text-4xl font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
			Pipe Lights
		</h1>
		<hr class="mt-6 border-0 border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800" />
	</section>

	<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-20 sm:pb-24">
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-start gap-12 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-10">
			<figure
				class="m-0 lg:col-span-4 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800/70 shadow-sm"
			>
				<img
					src={pipeLights.src}
					width={900}
					height={1200}
					alt="Pipe light in a room: PVC WYE and elbow fittings with purple accent lighting; hand adjusting the rotating elbow"
					class="aspect-[3/4] h-auto w-full object-cover sm:aspect-[4/5] lg:aspect-[3/4]"
					loading="eager"
					decoding="async"
				/>
			</figure>

			<div class="space-y-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 lg:col-span-3">
				<p>
					I love having objects that symbolize different chapters of my life. For me, work isn't
					something to avoid; it's an opportunity to express who I am.
				</p>
				<p>
					When our office was preparing to move, we planned to dispose of several sample items. I asked
					my manager if I could keep two 8-inch fittings, and he agreed.
				</p>
				<p>
					So, I designed this light: an art piece that I can display in my apartment. The elbow is
					connected to the WYE with a lazy Susan. The direction of the light can be adjusted with a
					single finger.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="m-0 lg:col-span-5">
				<img
					src={pipeRender.src}
					width={1200}
					height={800}
					alt="Exploded 3D view: diffusers, lamp and reflector in elbow, lazy Susan bearing between elbow and WYE base, side outlet lighting stack"
					class="h-auto w-full object-contain"
					loading="lazy"
					decoding="async"
				/>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<footer class="border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 bg-white dark:bg-zinc-950">
		<div
			class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4 px-6 py-10 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400"
		>
			<span>Bora Tavman — Pipe lights</span>
			<a
				href="/product-design"
				class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-50 underline decoration-zinc-300 dark:decoration-zinc-600 underline-offset-4 transition-colors hover:decoration-zinc-900 dark:hover:decoration-zinc-300"
			>
				Back to contents
			</a>
		</div>
	</footer>
</div>
